---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
	title="About | 10 Billion Travelers"
	description="Meet Kevin White — over 1 million miles traveled across 26 countries. Learn the story behind 10 Billion Travelers."
>
	<!-- Hero banner with about.jpeg background, fixed attachment -->
	<section class="about-hero">
		<div class="about-hero-inner">
			<h1 class="about-hero-title">Our Story</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Bio section: image left, text right -->
	<section class="bio-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="bio-grid">
				<div class="bio-image-col">
					<div class="bio-image-wrap">
						<img
							src="https://10btravelers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Kevin-White-1-283x300.jpeg"
							alt="Kevin White"
							width="283"
							height="300"
							class="bio-photo"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bio-text-col">
					<p>I was born to travel! I've logged over 1 million miles. Before I'm 100 years old there will be 10 Billion people alive. I'll inspire as many travelers as possible!</p>

					<p>Born in a poor family in Western North Carolina, I had only traveled outside of NC for a few days until I went to college in South Carolina. I didn't even have a passport until I was 30 years old. Today, I've logged over 1 million miles and have traveled to 26 different countries around the world.</p>

					<p>I love to travel. I love adventure. I love to travel to popular destinations but love even more to sleep under the stars where very few people have ever gone. I know how to travel. I know what makes airlines, hotels, restaurants, and attractions great! I'm blessed with a ton of practical travel experience and would love to share it with you.</p>

					<p>Check out our Vlogs, Blogs, Reviews, and Travel Services. We will inspire &amp; facilitate your travel dreams. Let us consult with you to make your hotel, restaurant, or attraction more profitable. Are your bags packed yet?</p>

					<h3 class="bio-name">Kevin White</h3>
					<p class="bio-caption">Having fun on the Great Wall</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA with background image -->
	<section class="about-cta">
		<div class="about-cta-box">
			<div class="about-cta-overlay"></div>
			<div class="about-cta-inner">
				<div class="about-cta-text">
					<h2>HAVE A QUESTION</h2>
					<p>WE'D LOVE TO HEAR FROM YOU</p>
				</div>
				<div class="about-cta-action">
					<a href="mailto:info@10btravelers.com" class="btn btn-cta">EMAIL US</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* About hero — background image with fixed attachment */
	.about-hero {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 400px;
		background: url("https://10btravelers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/about.jpeg") bottom center / cover no-repeat;
		background-attachment: fixed;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	.about-hero-inner {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 100px 0;
	}
	.about-hero-img-wrap {
		width: 214px;
		margin: 0 auto 24px;
	}
	.about-hero-portrait {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
	}
	.about-hero-title {
		color: #ffffff;
		font-size: 40px;
		text-align: center;
		letter-spacing: 2.5px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.about-hero { min-height: 300px; }
		.about-hero-title { font-size: 30px; }
		.about-hero-inner { padding: 60px 20px; }
	}

	/* Bio section */
	.bio-section {
		padding: 0;
		background: #ffffff;
	}
	.bio-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 40px;
		max-width: 90%;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 60px 50px;
		align-items: start;
	}
	.bio-image-col {
		padding-left: 60px;
		padding-top: 30px;
	}
	.bio-image-wrap {
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	.bio-image-wrap::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -24px;
		left: -48px;
		width: calc(17 * 24px);
		height: calc(11 * 24px);
		background-image: radial-gradient(#ADD8E6 2px, transparent 2px);
		background-size: 24px 24px;
		z-index: 0;
	}
	.bio-photo {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 10;
		width: 283px;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
	}
	.bio-text-col {
		padding-top: 0;
	}
	.bio-text-col p {
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}
	.bio-name {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		font-size: 23px;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: capitalize;
		margin-top: 20px;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	.bio-caption {
		font-size: 16px;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.bio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 50px 30px; }
		.bio-image-col { padding-left: 50px; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.bio-grid { padding: 30px 20px; max-width: 100%; }
		.bio-image-col { padding-left: 50px; }
		.bio-text-col p { font-size: 14px; }
		.bio-caption { font-size: 14px; }
	}

	/* About CTA */
	.about-cta {
		padding: 0 24px 40px;
	}
	.about-cta-box {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 15px;
		overflow: hidden;
		max-width: var(--container-max);
		margin: 0 auto;
		background: url("https://10btravelers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/10-Billion-Travelers-button-pic-1024x677.jpeg") bottom center / cover no-repeat;
	}
	.about-cta-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: #000000;
		opacity: 0.49;
	}
	.about-cta-inner {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 50px;
		gap: 32px;
	}
	.about-cta-text {
		flex: 1;
	}
	.about-cta-text h2 {
		color: var(--color-primary-hover);
		font-size: 55px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}
	.about-cta-text p {
		color: #ffffff;
		font-size: 20px;
		margin-top: 8px;
	}
	.about-cta-action {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	.btn-cta {
		background: var(--color-primary-hover);
		color: #ffffff;
		border-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
		border-radius: 5px;
		font-size: 15px;
	}
	.btn-cta:hover {
		background: var(--color-primary);
		border-color: var(--color-primary);
	}
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.about-cta-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 30px; }
		.about-cta-text h2 { font-size: 25px; }
		.about-cta-text p { font-size: 14px; }
	}
</style>
